OL,4,Cpredicted her own murder
OL,6,FA killer whose girlfriend predicted
OL,7,Fher own murder after months of abuse
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for at least 24 years.
OL,10,FWarren Spence fatally attacked Sam
OL,11,FVarley, 44, at their home in Brown
OL,12,FHill Terrace, Harehills, Leeds, in
OL,13,FFebruary last year.
OL,15,FLeeds Crown Court heard Ms Varley
OL,16,Fsuffered a catalogue of injuries
OL,17,Fincluding bite marks and 25 rib
OL,18,Ffractures.
OL,20,FShe had previously told police: "He's
OL,21,Fgoing to end up killing me."
