OL,4,Cpredicted her own murder
OL,6,FProsecutor Stephen Wood KC told the
OL,7,Fjury their relationship had been
OL,8,Fcharacterised by Spence's controlling
OL,9,Fbehaviour and use of "indiscriminate
OL,10,Fviolence".
OL,12,FShe visited a community centre seeking
OL,13,Fhelp for domestic abuse and told a
OL,14,Ffriend in a message: "He caught me,
OL,15,FI've got a battering."
OL,17,FFootage played in court showed a
OL,18,Fpolice conversation with Ms Varley on
OL,19,FNew Year's Eve 2023.
