OL,3,CLife for killer whose partner
OL,4,Cpredicted her own murder
OL,6,FShe could be heard saying "I can't say
OL,7,Fanything" when asked if the defendant
OL,8,Fhad hit her, adding: "He's just not a
OL,9,Fnice man... He's scared me.
OL,11,FMs Varley told officers she had "asked
OL,12,Ffor help".
OL,14,F"I'm screaming for help... He's going
OL,15,Fto end up killing me," she said in the
OL,16,Fvideo.
OL,18,FSpence was under investigation for
OL,19,Fviolence and damage to their property
OL,20,Fwhen he murdered Ms Varley.
