OL,3,CLife for killer whose partner
OL,4,Cpredicted her own murder
OL,6,FHer body was found on 12 February
OL,7,Fafter a family member raised concerns
OL,8,Ffor her welfare.
OL,10,FSpence was arrested in Scarborough
OL,11,Fthree days later.
OL,13,FHe denied murder, but was found guilty
OL,14,Fafter the trial.
OL,16,FJudge Cotter told him: "You remain a
OL,17,Frisk to women as long as you are able
OL,18,Fto be violent to anybody."
