OL,6,FWest Yorkshire Police said a domestic
OL,7,Fhomicide review was being carried out
OL,8,Finto the case to "identify any lessons
OL,9,Fto be learned".
OL,11,FThe force has referred itself to the
OL,12,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,13,Fbecause of the contact officers had
OL,14,Fwith the couple before Ms Varley's
OL,15,Fmurder.
