OL,6,FDet Ch Insp James Entwistle said:
OL,7,F"West Yorkshire Police remains
OL,8,Fcommitted to working alongside our
OL,9,Fpartner agencies to tackle violence
OL,10,Fagainst women and girls, particularly
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse, and we urge victims or
OL,12,Fthose who know about their situation
OL,13,Fto report it to us."
