OL,6,FIn a statement the family of Sam
OL,7,FVarley said: "Sam's death has had a
OL,8,Fdevastating impact on all our family,
OL,9,Fmore so as we've learned the awful
OL,10,Fcircumstances in which she was taken
OL,11,Ffrom us and the suffering she endured
OL,12,Fat the hands of what we can only
OL,13,Fdescribe as an absolute monster.
OL,15,F"Although Sam's death will remain a
OL,16,Fheartache forever, her family choose
OL,17,Fto remember her for the beautiful,
OL,18,Fkind, loving and funny girl she really
OL,19,Fwas, our Sam."
